options.title: White sock
options.description: A unique and eye-catching freshwater shrimp species, distinguished by the bright white coloration on its lower legs, giving the appearance of "socks", which stand out dramatically against its darker body. This shrimp, originating from the Sulawesi region of Indonesia, has a slender, elongated body that typically displays a dark, bold color paletteâ€”ranging from jet black to deep burgundy or brown.
